{
  "stem": "12051.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She was from Warsaw, very intelligent girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She had two containers, so she used to come for the soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She said, for Elsa and for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She figured she will get away with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Many times she got away with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she got two soups, which was-- you could give somebody a diamond, it wouldn't have been as precious as that extra soup.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] All right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That was when we were Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we worked hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we had no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we were, by that point, already giving up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was three and a half years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And you cannot imagine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The winters were cold, and you had no shoes and no clothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "A rag that I cleaned the machine I stole, and I wrapped my feet into it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "People had only wooden shoes by then because they wouldn't give you leather shoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So they had those step-ins like the Dutch clogs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And, and I-- and that's how we lived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes a, a Polish worker would tell you something, that Stalingrad fell, or this is going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told us the Warsaw Ghetto burned, and, and there is no more ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Jews are all killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we knew that we are in a big predicament.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1945, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had birthday on the 15th of January.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother said, Gerda, I promise you that one day, you will still wear a suit made by a tailor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, Mommy, you're dreaming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're really dreaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, how can you say it to me?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't have a pair of shoes on my feet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you're promising me-- OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the 16th of January, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we ran away-- a group of 11 people.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
